Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}過ぎるだけの時間じゃ悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:42.76,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}刻まなくちゃ　ここにいると心が叫ぶ瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.22,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}I am dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:48.39,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}迷いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:51.93,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}涙を飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.52,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}不器用だね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:58.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:04.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大空を見上げ何も言えず
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:12.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}胸が痛む訳考えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:14.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:17.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}風を走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:23.42,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君と僕の仲で何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}わからないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:33.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}キラキラ光る太陽が照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:38.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}永遠など　知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:33.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}后悔浪费了过去的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:42.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}必须在这里刻下心灵吼叫的那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}I am dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:48.39,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直很迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:51.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}强忍着泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.52,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:58.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}连梦想也与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:04.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}看着天空一句话也说不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:12.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直思考着胸口的那股痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:14.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:17.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}追赶着清风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:23.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}你与我之间发生了什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}虽然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:33.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}向着那耀眼的太阳所照耀之处前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:38.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}永远什么的 我才不知道呢
